  "tabs": [
    {
      "id": "diag",
      "label": "Diagnóstico",
      "html": "<div class=\"slbl\">Critérios diagnósticos de CAD</div>\n      <table class=\"drug-table\"><thead><tr><th>Parâmetro</th><th>CAD ligeira</th><th>CAD moderada</th><th>CAD grave</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n        <tr><td><span class=\"dn\">Glicemia mg/dL</span></td><td>&gt;250</td><td>&gt;250</td><td>&gt;250</td></tr>\n        <tr><td><span class=\"dn\">pH arterial</span></td><td>7,25–7,30</td><td>7,00–7,24</td><td>&lt;7,00</td></tr>\n        <tr><td><span class=\"dn\">Bicarbonato mEq/L</span></td><td>15–18</td><td>10–14</td><td>&lt;10</td></tr>\n        <tr><td><span class=\"dn\">Cetonúria/cetonemia</span></td><td>Positiva</td><td>Positiva</td><td>Positiva</td></tr>\n        <tr><td><span class=\"dn\">Hiato aniónico</span></td><td>&gt;10</td><td>&gt;12</td><td>&gt;12</td></tr>\n        <tr><td><span class=\"dn\">Estado de consciência</span></td><td>Alerta</td><td>Alerta/sonolento</td><td>Estupor/coma</td></tr>\n      </tbody></table>\n      <div class=\"slbl\" style=\"margin-top:12px\">Causa precipitante — investigar sempre</div>\n      <div class=\"nf-grid\">\n        <div class=\"nf-item\"><strong>As 5 I&#39;s</strong>Infeção (mais comum) · Insulina insuficiente · Infarte (EAM) · Intoxicação · Ignorância (não adesão)</div>\n        <div class=\"nf-item\"><strong>Exames urgentes</strong>Gasimetria arterial · Ionograma (K+!) · Ureia/creatinina · Cetonemia/cetonúria · ECG · Rx tórax · Culturas se suspeita infecção</div>\n      </div>"
    },
    {
      "id": "alg",
      "label": "Algoritmo — Tratamento",
      "html": "<div class=\"alert alert-red\"><span class=\"alert-icon\">⚠️</span><div class=\"alert-text\"><b>Potássio antes de insulina!</b> Se K+ &lt;3,5 mEq/L → repor K+ primeiro, depois iniciar insulina. Insulina sem K+ adequado → hipocaliemia fatal.</div></div>\n      <div class=\"linha-block\">\n        <div class=\"linha-head\"><span class=\"linha-pill lp-lp\" style=\"background:var(--red-bg);color:var(--red-text);border-color:var(--red-border)\">Passo 1 — Fluidoterapia</span><span class=\"linha-name\">1.ª hora: reposição volémica agressiva</span></div>\n        <div class=\"cards-grid\">\n          <div class=\"drug-card star\"><div class=\"star-label\">1.ª hora — expansão volómica</div>\n            <div class=\"drug-row\"><div><div class=\"drug-name\">NaCl 0,9%</div><div class=\"drug-mol\">Soro fisiológico</div></div></div>\n            <div class=\"drug-body\"><b>1 L NaCl 0,9% na 1.ª hora IV.</b> Depois 500 mL/h × 2–4h. Quando glicemia &lt;200 mg/dL → mudar para SG 5% (ou Dx 5%) para evitar hipoglicemia durante insulina.</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"rule\"></div>\n      <div class=\"linha-block\">\n        <div class=\"linha-head\"><span class=\"linha-pill lp-2\">Passo 2 — Potássio</span><span class=\"linha-name\">Repor ANTES de insulina se K+ &lt;5 mEq/L</span></div>\n        <div class=\"cards-grid\">\n          <div class=\"drug-card star\"><div class=\"star-label\">Reposição de K+ obrigatória</div>\n            <div class=\"drug-row\"><div><div class=\"drug-name\">Cloreto de potássio IV</div><div class=\"drug-mol\">KCl Braun® perfusão</div></div></div>\n            <div class=\"drug-body\"><b>K+ &lt;3,5 → 40 mEq/h IV (aguardar K+≥3,5 antes de insulina).</b> K+ 3,5–5,0 → 20–40 mEq/h IV. K+ &gt;5,0 → sem KCl, iniciar insulina, monitorizar. Monitorizar K+ a cada 2h nas primeiras 6h.</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"rule\"></div>\n      <div class=\"linha-block\">\n        <div class=\"linha-head\"><span class=\"linha-pill lp-1\">Passo 3 — Insulina</span><span class=\"linha-name\">Iniciar após K+≥3,5 mEq/L confirmado</span></div>\n        <div class=\"cards-grid\">\n          <div class=\"drug-card star\"><div class=\"star-label\">Insulina IV — padrão de tratamento</div>\n            <div class=\"drug-row\"><div><div class=\"drug-name\">Insulina Regular IV perfusão</div><div class=\"drug-mol\">Actrapid® · Humulin R®</div></div></div>\n            <div class=\"drug-body\"><b>0,1 U/kg/h IV</b> (sem bólus inicial). Objectivo: descida de glicemia 50–75 mg/dL/hora. Se descida &lt;50 mg/dL/hora na 1.ª hora → dobrar débito. Quando glicemia &lt;200 mg/dL → reduzir para 0,05 U/kg/h + adicionar glicose IV.</div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"alert alert-green\" style=\"margin-top:10px\"><span class=\"alert-icon\">✅</span><div class=\"alert-text\"><b>Critérios de resolução CAD:</b> Glicemia &lt;200 + pH &gt;7,30 + bicarbonato &gt;18 + hiato aniónico &lt;12. <b>Transição para SC:</b> iniciar insulina SC 2h antes de suspender IV. Investigar e tratar sempre a causa precipitante.</div></div>"
    },
    {
      "id": "calc_cad",
      "label": "Calculadoras",
      "html": "<style>.calc-box{background:var(--surface-2,#f8f9fa);border:1px solid var(--border,#dee2e6);border-radius:10px;padding:16px;margin-bottom:14px}.calc-title{font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:var(--text-primary,#1a1a2e);margin-bottom:12px}.calc-item{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:7px 0;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border,#dee2e6)}.calc-item:last-of-type{border-bottom:none}.calc-item input[type=checkbox]{width:16px;height:16px;accent-color:var(--blue,#2563eb);cursor:pointer;flex-shrink:0}.calc-item input[type=number]{width:80px;border:1px solid var(--border,#dee2e6);border-radius:6px;padding:3px 7px;font-size:13px;background:var(--surface,#fff);color:var(--text-primary)}.calc-label{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-primary);flex:1;cursor:pointer}.calc-pts{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted,#6b7280);white-space:nowrap}.calc-sel{border:1px solid var(--border,#dee2e6);border-radius:6px;padding:3px 7px;font-size:13px;background:var(--surface,#fff);color:var(--text-primary,#1a1a2e);max-width:260px}.calc-result{margin-top:14px;padding:12px 16px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;text-align:center;transition:all .3s}.calc-result.r-low{background:var(--green-bg,#f0fdf4);color:var(--green,#16a34a);border:1px solid var(--green-border,#bbf7d0)}.calc-result.r-mod{background:var(--amber-bg,#fffbeb);color:var(--amber,#d97706);border:1px solid var(--amber-border,#fde68a)}.calc-result.r-high{background:var(--red-bg,#fef2f2);color:var(--red,#dc2626);border:1px solid var(--red-border,#fecaca)}.calc-result.r-none{background:var(--surface-2,#f8f9fa);color:var(--text-muted,#6b7280);border:1px solid var(--border,#dee2e6)}.calc-link{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;font-size:12px;color:var(--blue,#2563eb);text-decoration:none;margin-top:10px;padding:5px 10px;border:1px solid var(--blue-border,#bfdbfe);border-radius:6px;background:var(--blue-bg,#eff6ff)}</style>\n      <div class=\"slbl\">Calculadoras &mdash; Cetoacidose Diab&eacute;tica</div>\n      <div class=\"calc-box\">\n        <div class=\"calc-title\">Gap Ani&oacute;nico (Anion Gap) com corre&ccedil;&atilde;o para albumina</div>\n        <div class=\"calc-item\"><label class=\"calc-label\">S&oacute;dio (Na&#8314;) mEq/L</label><input type=\"number\" id=\"ag_na\" value=\"140\" min=\"100\" max=\"180\" oninput=\"calcAG()\" class=\"calc-sel\" style=\"max-width:90px\"></div>\n        <div class=\"calc-item\"><label class=\"calc-label\">Cloro (Cl&#8315;) mEq/L</label><input type=\"number\" id=\"ag_cl\" value=\"102\" min=\"70\" max=\"140\" oninput=\"calcAG()\" class=\"calc-sel\" style=\"max-width:90px\"></div>\n        <div class=\"calc-item\"><label class=\"calc-label\">Bicarbonato (HCO&#8323;&#8315;) mEq/L</label><input type=\"number\" id=\"ag_hco3\" value=\"24\" min=\"1\" max=\"40\" oninput=\"calcAG()\" class=\"calc-sel\" style=\"max-width:90px\"></div>\n        <div class=\"calc-item\"><label class=\"calc-label\">Albumina s&eacute;rica (g/dL)</label><input type=\"number\" id=\"ag_alb\" value=\"4.0\" min=\"1\" max=\"6\" step=\"0.1\" oninput=\"calcAG()\" class=\"calc-sel\" style=\"max-width:90px\"></div>\n        <div id=\"res_ag\" class=\"calc-result r-none\">Introduza os valores</div>\n        <a href=\"https://www.mdcalc.com/calc/1669/anion-gap\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"calc-link\">&#128279; MDCalc &mdash; Anion Gap online</a>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"calc-box\">\n        <div class=\"calc-title\">Classifica&ccedil;&atilde;o de gravidade da CAD</div>\n        <div class=\"calc-item\"><label class=\"calc-label\">pH arterial</label><select id=\"cad_ph\" onchange=\"calcCAD()\" class=\"calc-sel\"><option value=\"0\">Seleccionar</option><option value=\"1\">&ge;7,30 (ligeira)</option><option value=\"2\">7,00&ndash;7,29 (moderada)</option><option value=\"3\">&lt;7,00 (grave)</option></select></div>\n        <div class=\"calc-item\"><label class=\"calc-label\">HCO&#8323;&#8315; (mEq/L)</label><select id=\"cad_hco3\" onchange=\"calcCAD()\" class=\"calc-sel\"><option value=\"0\">Seleccionar</option><option value=\"1\">15&ndash;18 (ligeira)</option><option value=\"2\">10&ndash;14 (moderada)</option><option value=\"3\">&lt;10 (grave)</option></select></div>\n        <div class=\"calc-item\"><label class=\"calc-label\">Estado mental</label><select id=\"cad_em\" onchange=\"calcCAD()\" class=\"calc-sel\"><option value=\"0\">Seleccionar</option><option value=\"1\">Alerta (ligeira)</option><option value=\"2\">Alerta/sonolento (moderada)</option><option value=\"3\">Est&uacute;por/coma (grave)</option></select></div>\n        <div id=\"res_cad\" class=\"calc-result r-none\">Seleccione os valores</div>\n      </div>\n      <script>\n      function calcAG(){\n        var na=parseFloat(document.getElementById(\"ag_na\").value)||0;\n        var cl=parseFloat(document.getElementById(\"ag_cl\").value)||0;\n        var hco3=parseFloat(document.getElementById(\"ag_hco3\").value)||0;\n        var alb=parseFloat(document.getElementById(\"ag_alb\").value)||4.0;\n        var ag=na-cl-hco3;\n        var agCorr=ag+2.5*(4.0-alb);\n        var el=document.getElementById(\"res_ag\");\n        var cls=agCorr>12?\"r-high\":\"r-low\";\n        var txt=\"GA = \"+ag.toFixed(1)+\" | GA corrigido = \"+agCorr.toFixed(1)+\" mEq/L\";\n        txt+=agCorr>12?\" → ELEVADO (normal 8–12) — considerar CAD, acidose láctica, intoxicação\":\" → Normal (8–12 mEq/L)\";\n        el.className=\"calc-result \"+cls;el.textContent=txt;\n      }\n      function calcCAD(){\n        var ph=parseInt(document.getElementById(\"cad_ph\").value)||0;\n        var hco3=parseInt(document.getElementById(\"cad_hco3\").value)||0;\n        var em=parseInt(document.getElementById(\"cad_em\").value)||0;\n        if(!ph||!hco3||!em){document.getElementById(\"res_cad\").textContent=\"Seleccione todos os valores\";return;}\n        var mx=Math.max(ph,hco3,em);\n        var el=document.getElementById(\"res_cad\");var cls,txt;\n        if(mx===1){cls=\"r-low\";txt=\"CAD LIGEIRA — pH ≥7,30 · HCO₃ 15–18 · Alerta → SU, insulinoterapia\";}\n        else if(mx===2){cls=\"r-mod\";txt=\"CAD MODERADA — pH 7,00–7,29 · HCO₃ 10–14 → Internamento, insulina IV\";}\n        else{cls=\"r-high\";txt=\"CAD GRAVE — pH <7,00 · HCO₃ <10 · Obnubilado → UCI\";}\n        el.className=\"calc-result \"+cls;el.textContent=txt;\n      }\n      setTimeout(function(){calcAG();},200);\n      </script>"
    },
    {
      "id": "alarme",
      "label": "Sinais de alarme",
      "html": "<div class=\"alarm-list\">\n        <div class=\"alarm-item\"><div class=\"adot\"></div><span>Edema cerebral (raro mas fatal) — mais em crianças: cefaleias + deterioração neurológica durante tratamento → manitol 0,5–1 g/kg IV</span></div>\n        <div class=\"alarm-item\"><div class=\"adot\"></div><span>Hipocaliemia grave (K+ &lt;2,5) → arritmias fatais → repor urgente antes de qualquer insulina</span></div>\n        <div class=\"alarm-item\"><div class=\"adot\"></div><span>CAD euglicémica (glicemia normal mas cetose) → cada vez mais frequente com iSGLT2 — atenção ao diagnóstico</span></div>\n        <div class=\"alarm-item\"><div class=\"adot\"></div><span>Acidose grave pH &lt;7,0 refractária → bicarbonato 50 mEq IV lento apenas se pH &lt;6,9 + compromisso hemodinâmico</span></div>\n      </div>"
    }
  ]
}